Step 1 :
Open a new terminal and type arduino to open arduino (DO NOT CLOSE THE TERMINAL)
Step 2 :
Open the sketch below by choosing ros_lib -> HelloWorld from the Arduino examples menu and upload the code into Arduino
Step 3 :
Open another new terminal and execute the below command : (DO NOT CLOSE THE TERMINAL)
roscore
Step 4 : 
Open another new terminal and execute the below command : (DO NOT CLOSE THE TERMINAL)
rosrun rosserial_python serial_node.py /dev/ttyUSB0
Step 5 : 
Open another new terminal and execute the below command : (DO NOT CLOSE THE TERMINAL)
rostopic echo chatter



